    <h2><u><i>Primary Services</i></u></h2>
<font face="Tahoma" size="4" color="#00000">
       
<li>Precision Crop Management: We use GPS and satellite imagery to monitor your crops and planting.<br>
     
<li>Pest & Disease Management: We create solutions for your specific crop that will help protect crops and reduce losses.<br>
      
<li>Personalized Fertilizer Solutions: We will create custom fertilizer based on your specific soil and crop needs.<br>
      
<li>Soil Health Analysis & Improvement: We test soil for organic material, pH levels, and nutrient levels.<br>
     
<li>Smart Irrigation Systems: We will use sensors and automated controls to run a watering system based on climate and weather.<br>
      
<li>Harvest Planning and Forecasting: We will plan resource allocation and make decisions throughout your entire harvest season. </li><br>

